title: The Internet Destroys This Photo of 13 Republicans Giving a Thumbs Up
text: — rob delaney (@robdelaney) February 17, 2017 who's got two thumbs and has never found the clit? pic.twitter.com/5HSsUIoyEs — Alison Stevenson (@JustAboutGlad) February 17, 2017 "Thumbs up if you'd slaughter your children for political gain." pic.twitter.com/P0sJqI517W — Amanda M-W (@Manda_like_wine) February 17, 2017 thumbs up 4 dying on the toilet pic.twitter.com/pTrAO5HLpT — Bill Corbett (@BillCorbett) February 17, 2017 Casting call for new Dick Tracy villain Donny Two Thumbs pic.twitter.com/pF7Z56VbPl — Tim Strube (@timmyjoe) February 17, 2017 @POTUS who's got two thumbs and doesn't know what the fuck they're doing? These guys! — Trump Troller (@TrumpTrolling17) February 17, 2017 If you’re able to look past the thumbs and the overwhelming whiteness , however, a few more Easter eggs are buried in the shot. Look at the left hand of the man standing to the left of the guy in the orange tie. Is he trying to reach out and touch the president? Did he forget how to make a thumbs up with both hands at once? The world may never know. @TUSK81 @POTUS pence's brown shoes with black suit are only the 5th worst thing about that pic — AJ LENAR (@AJASONLENAR) February 17, 2017 Composition is all off, among other things. pic.twitter.com/KpMaONFD0W — Annie Lowrey (@AnnieLowrey) February 17, 2017 And just in case that wasn’t enough to look at, one Twitter user opted to add a little something to the foreground. — SENATOR HORSE PISS (@TriviumPaolo) February 17, 2017 Rule of thumb: If a dick can be added to a photo, a dick will be added to the photo.
